    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Sorcerer Bloodline</strong><br/><br/><p>You were born with the power of earth genies, and the magic of the shaitans is strong in you.</p><p><b>Class Skill: </b>Knowledge (planes).</p><p><b>Bonus Spells: </b>true strike (3rd), glitterdust (5th), greater magic weapon (7th), stoneskin (9th), wall of stone (11th), wall of iron (13th), plane shift (15th), iron body (17th), wish (19th).</p><p><b>Bonus Feats: </b>Dodge, Empower Spell, Great Fortitude, Improved Initiative, Lightning Reflexes, Power Attack, Skill Focus (Knowledge [planes]), Weapon Finesse.</p><p><b>Bloodline Arcana: </b>Whenever you cast a spell that deals energy damage, you can change the type of damage to acid. This effect also changes the spell's descriptors to match this energy type.</p><p><b>Bloodline Powers: </b>Like a shaitan, you have both natural power over earth, and several other genie-based abilities.</p>",
